    <abstract>
      <t>This document describes a set of recommendations to use when implementing ACE/OAuth 2.0 clients that are working in disadvantaged networks. Issues such as token revocation have a much higher priority in scenarios where Resource Servers are IoT devices, and network connectivity is limited and intermittent.</t>
